### Selected article:
**Title:** [Gastroenteropancreatic Neuroendocrine Tumor Incidence by Sex and Age in the US](https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamaoncology/fullarticle/2829036?guestAccessKey=67da1586-c86b-42ff-ba07-a71fa4cf6c5e&utm_source=twitter&utm_medium=social_jamaonc&utm_term=15837949917&utm_campaign=article_alert&linkId=717449692)  
**Journal:** JAMA Oncology  
**Authors:** Yazan Abboud, Anand Shah, Riya Sutariya, et al.
**Year:** 2025  
**PMID:** [39821008](https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39821008/)   
**DOI:** [10.1001/jamaoncol.2024.5937](https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39821008/). 


<br><br>

### The original figure
![Visual abstract](w14_org.jpg)



<br>

### Import libraries
```{r, echo = TRUE}

# Define the required package names
packages <- c("tidyverse", "scales", "fabricatr", "glue", 
              "cowplot",
              "finalfit",
              "survminer", "survival")

# Function to check, install, and load packages
load_packages <- function(packages) {
        
  for (package in packages) {
    if (!require(package, character.only = TRUE)) {
        install.packages(package)
        library(package, character.only = TRUE)
    } else {
      # suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(package, character.only = TRUE))
        library(package, character.only = TRUE)
    }
  }
}

load_packages(packages)


theme_set(theme_light(base_family = "Helvetica"))



```

<br>




### Prepare fabricated data 
(Claude 3.7 Sonnet was used to extract data from the original figure)  

```{r}
library(fabricatr)  
library(tidyverse)  
library(cowplot)  

# Create the pancreas dataset with all demographics and years  
pancreas_data <- fabricate(  
  N = 5 * 19,  # 5 demographics, 19 years  
  Organ = "Pancreas",  
  Demographic = rep(c("Overall", "Male", "Female", "Older adults", "Young adults"), each = 19),  
  Year = rep(2001:2019, times = 5),  
  IncidenceRate = c(  
    # Overall  
    0.35, 0.35, 0.36, 0.37, 0.38, 0.40, 0.43, 0.46, 0.49, 0.52,   
    0.56, 0.65, 0.85, 0.95, 1.05, 1.10, 1.15, 1.20, 1.20,  
